## 5. KNOWN BUGS (🐛 MUST FIX)

### Bug 1: Parent Chat Stuck on "Loading chat..."
**Symptom:** Parent dashboard shows "Loading chat..." forever when clicking "Chat with Teacher"  
**Root Cause:** The `/api/chat/parent/conversations` endpoint uses a 3-step teacher resolution:
1. Check `student.teacherId` — often `null` because teachers don't always get assigned as `teacherId` on the student record
2. Find teacher with `classTeacherFor` matching student's class — requires `isClassTeacher: true`
3. Find any teacher with `classAssignments` matching — this should work but the student's `section` field or teacher's `classAssignments` might not match exactly

**Fix Location:** [routes/chat.js](file:///d:/Internship/Atkool%20as%20Agents%20folder/atkool-website/routes/chat.js) lines 220-297  
**Fix Strategy:**
1. Add `try/catch` around the entire `loadParentChat()` function in [parent-dashboard.html](file:///d:/Internship/Atkool%20as%20Agents%20folder/atkool-website/public/parent-dashboard.html) (line 351) to show an error message instead of hanging
2. In the backend, relax the section matching — try without section if exact match fails
3. When a teacher adds a student, auto-set `student.teacherId` to that teacher's ID

